## File Mapping Convention

| Cypress source | Playwright target |
|---------------|-------------------|
| `cypress/views/selector-*.ts` | Locators inside `playwright/src/page-objects/<feature>-page.ts` |
| `cypress/views/<feature>-flow.ts` | `playwright/src/page-objects/<feature>-page.ts` (interactions) + `playwright/src/step-drivers/<feature>-step-driver.ts` (step wrappers) |
| `cypress/views/actions.ts` | `playwright/src/page-objects/vm-actions-page.ts` or method in relevant page object |
| `cypress/views/modals.ts` | Methods within relevant page objects (modal interactions belong to the page that triggers them) |
| `cypress/views/tab.ts` | `navigateToTab()` methods on page objects that have tabs |
| `cypress/support/commands.ts` | Split: navigation → page objects, K8s → `KubernetesClient`, login → `LoginStepDriver` |
| `cypress/support/nav.ts` | `navigate*` methods on page objects |
| `cypress/support/selectors.ts` | `BasePage` utilities and page object locators |
| `cypress/types/*.ts` | `playwright/src/types/` or inline in page objects |
| `cypress/utils/const/*.ts` | `playwright/src/utils/constants/` or `EnvVariables` |
| `cypress/tests/<tier>/<feature>/*.cy.ts` | `playwright/tests/<tier>/<feature>/<test>.spec.ts` |

